=head1 DESCRIPTION

The structure used to configure the list of database patterns in source
database endpoint for Firehose to read from.

Amazon Data Firehose is in preview release and is subject to change.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Exclude => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The list of database patterns in source database endpoint to be
excluded for Firehose to read from.

Amazon Data Firehose is in preview release and is subject to change.


=head2 Include => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The list of database patterns in source database endpoint to be
